  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542190/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765120665\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542190/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765120665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542190/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765120665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2>Player character is Rhino man and his mission in this platformer/runner game is to find balloons in different levels. 8 Different maps. Levels contain moving objects, rotating objects, moving deathly traps like moving spikes and moving balls. Also falling from map or if player hit water, player is killed and level need start again. So be a hero and make accurate jumps to avoid traps and find balls<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>- 9 maps<br>- Deathly traps like moving spikes<br>- Falling out of map or hitting water will kill player<br>- Rotating objects",
